node.text:
7 years ago I made “Tumblr Girls” in an air bnb when I was living out of a suitcase working on my first album - unsigned - telling stories I hadn’t even got the chance to personally live yet. I was still a kid on the outside chasing a dream.

I appreciate your patience over the last few years as I’ve been trying to put my all into making sure this album does it all justice. I appreciate every step of the journey and every single person who’s been a part of it.

node.text: One of my favorite songs off the album I literally can’t wait to finally get to share this one with the world. This album is a full circle journey from where we started to where we are now. Grateful and appreciative for everyone who’s been along for the ride. Next chapter starts tomorrow ❤️
